{"tid":1507281,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"是日記者會必問","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:30:08.000Z","uid":301432,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7d668f8b887bc05b271de36d8ea5b6d7410e8ab2","tid":1507281,"uid":301432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<strong> - 就警員昨晚舉槍指向市民及記者，昨日回覆指情況電光火石，<br />\n   生死一線，同事生命受成脅必須開槍平亂。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">   但為何元朗721時，市民生死一線，生命受嚴重威脅，<br />\n   卻沒有開槍平亂，反而調頭離開?</span></strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n - 就警員昨晚踢向跪在地上的街坊，昨日回覆指動作自然反應。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">   那請問如果有人在市民面前跪下有動作(如表演,行乞或其他活動)，<br />\n   市民是否可一腳踢向他，而不受法律制裁?<br />\n   如果此情況應交由法庭判決，是否指該涉案警員案件應交由法庭判決?<br />\n   還是警員執法時，將不受基本法的任何規管?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申: 琴晚無睇曬記者會"},{"pid":"f002632c3d6c55dc2fde9ec34e9d4081fd2c81ab","tid":1507281,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=5193a4c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"e9143716a194b97cd2ab60f2c950702b6921df0f","tid":1507281,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:41:53.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1．13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=fac252f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04wmZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04wmZVM.jpg&h=efdc3dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b22ce22629c39aa72f895008da580b07025202f","tid":1507281,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff99f9fb204443aff7251e285d